## Orders [/v1/orders]

### List [GET]

Lists basic information of Orders for a quick table view to drill-down into
orders further.

+ Request (application/json)
+ Response 200 (application/json)
  + Attributes (OrderList)

### Search [GET /v1/orders/search?term={term}]

Searches order by reference number or related customer name.

+ Parameters
    + term: `ABC-123` (required, string) - refNum or customer name, should be at least 2 characters
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (OrderList)

### Create [POST]

Creates a cart for an existing customer (or guest account) when `customerId`
given or creates a cart along with a new guest account when `email` is given.

+ Request (application/json)
    + Attributes (CreateCartPayload)
+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (FullOrder)
+ Response 400 (application/json)
    + Attributes (Errors)

